											<h2>What is SOUL TOKEN</h2>
									  </header>
									  <p>SOUL TOKEN is a charity crypto token on the Binance Smart Chain that aims to contribute <br>
									through charitable contributions all around the world. Every transaction has a 5% automatic liquidity fee and a 5% redistribution fee to holders. <br>
<br>
<br>

								5,000,000,000 OF Tokens will be allocated for donations every while, and to avoid price drops the donations will be regulated.
									We believe that through technology, everyone deservers to live a good life and with crypto tokens its easier than ever to help those in need.</p>
	
