								<header class="major">
									  <h2>How to Buy</h2>
								</header>
									<h5>Buy SOUL TOKEN on PancakeSwap through Trust wallet</h5> 
								<div><h2>Step 1: Create a Wallet</h2><p>Download <a href="https://trustwallet.com/" class="text-info" target="_blank">Trust Wallet</a> and create a wallet, Never share the secret phrase with anyone!<span class="text-warning">&nbsp;Make sure to copy the contract address of the token</span></p><div class="input-group mb-4 shadow-none" style="max-width:700px"><div style="color:#FFFFFF">Address</div></div><input type="text" value="0x44528da098b3cb58da3723b6175087ad6234e3e0" ><hr><h2 class="text-info">Step 2: Add SOUL TOKEN to the Wallet</h2><p>Tap the icon in the top-right and tap "Add Custom Token".</p><center><img src="images/trust1.jpg" width="250" height="60"></center><br>
<center><img src="images/trust2.jpg" width="250" height="500"></center><p>At the top, tap "Ethereum" next to Network, and change it to "Smart Chain". Copy the contract address paste it in the Contract Address field.</p><center><img src="images/trust3.jpg" width="250" height="500"></center><p>then</p><p>Click "Done" at the top and you should now have SOUL TOKEN added to your wallet!</p></div>
									<h2>Step 3: Buy or Send BNB(BSC)</h2>
									<p>On Trust Wallet Click on Smart Chain, then click on buy OR send BNB on the Binance smart Chain (BSC Network) to your Trust wallet</p>
									
									<h2>Step 4: Convert BNB to SOUL TOKEN</h2>
									<p>Go to DApps (Android) at the bottom of the main screen or the Browser on iPhones</p>
									<p>Open PancakeSwap in DApps or IOS Browser, then Connect your Trust Wallet by clicking on the top-right " Connect  " button. Scroll down to the "Exchange" section</p>
									<a href="https://community.trustwallet.com/t/using-walletconnect-to-access-pancakeswap/212307">Click here to see How to Connect pancakeswap to trust wallet on IOS in details</a>
									<p>Select BNB in the first slot, and in the second slot Paste the address of SOUL token</p>
									<img src="images/panc.jpg" width="250" height="500">
									<p>Then Click the settings ( <i class="fas fa-sliders-h"></i> ) icon and set the slippage to 12% or more for the transaction to clear.</p>
									<p>And Finally Click on SWAP!</p>
									
